<Layout
  title="About FastClickTest — Free Online CPS Test Tool"
  description="Learn about FastClickTest.com — the cleanest, most accurate free click speed test online. Built for gamers, Minecraft players, and anyone testing their CPS."
  currentPage="about"
>
<div class="page">

  <div class="page-hero">
    <h1>About <span class="hi">FastClickTest</span></h1>
    <p>The cleanest, most complete free click speed test on the internet — built for gamers, by gamers.</p>
  </div>

  <section class="seo-content" style="max-width:720px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 20px 60px;">
    <h2>About FastClickTest.com</h2>
    <p>FastClickTest.com is a free, browser-based click speed testing platform designed for gamers, esports players, and anyone interested in measuring and improving their clicking performance. We provide accurate, reliable testing tools that work directly in your browser — no downloads, no accounts, no fees. Ever.</p>

    <h3>Why We Built FastClickTest</h3>
    <p>We built FastClickTest because we noticed that most existing click speed test tools either had intrusive ads that blocked the test area, inaccurate measurement systems, or poor mobile experiences. We wanted to create the best possible click speed testing experience — clean, fast, accurate, and available on any device.</p>
    <p>Every test on FastClickTest uses high-precision timestamp measurement with sub-millisecond accuracy. Our scoring algorithm accounts for the full test duration (not just active clicking intervals) to give you the most honest CPS representation. We also store your personal best scores locally in your browser so you can track improvement over time without needing an account.</p>

    <h3>Our Tools</h3>
    <p><strong>CPS Click Speed Test</strong> — The main event. Test your clicks per second across 1, 5, 10, 15, 30-second, and 100-click challenge modes. Includes a live graph showing your CPS over time.</p>
    <p><strong>Jitter Click Test</strong> — Specifically designed for jitter clicking technique testing, with guidance on how to jitter click effectively.</p>
    <p><strong>Butterfly Click Test</strong> — Measures your butterfly clicking CPS with technique tips for this popular advanced method.</p>
    <p><strong>Drag Click Test</strong> — Tests hardware-assisted drag clicking for players exploring this high-CPS technique.</p>
    <p><strong>Right Click Speed Test</strong> — Measures your right mouse button click speed separately from your primary click.</p>
    <p><strong>Spacebar Speed Test</strong> — Tests your keyboard spacebar tapping speed for rhythm game and Minecraft players.</p>
    <p><strong>Reaction Time Test</strong> — Measures your visual reaction time in milliseconds to help you track your gaming reflexes.</p>

    <h3>Privacy and Data</h3>
    <p>FastClickTest does not collect, store, or transmit any personal data. Your test scores are stored locally in your browser using localStorage and never leave your device. We use Google Analytics for anonymous, aggregate traffic data only. Read our <a href="/privacy-policy">Privacy Policy</a> for full details.</p>

    <h3>Contact</h3>
    <p>Have a suggestion, bug report, or question? We read every message. <a href="/contact">Get in touch here</a>.</p>
  </section>
</Layout>